ces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10d7178bc3e16c9671a6ad8538da4f34451e8c8","tid":2031781,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cdbfb476654cc1007a77026f584c6ce48dc134","tid":2031781,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家一窩蜂去討論獨立後想點 <br />\n或者香港國旗要點點點<br />\n呢啲一啲都唔重要！<br />\n<br />\n最重要係 <br />\n想令到獨立成事 <br />\n民族自強嘅覺悟係先決條件！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【心態Gear up】當務之急 係鞏固香港嘅民族性<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2031619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2031619</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"56e8a3e2abbc75c522c0d3115a3e9e44b68850f8","tid":2031781,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"Cap圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361ce76804ac1a220d83174d0b9c63a87f80177c","tid":2031781,"uid":46170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:00:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c0a5adfd4122865302bc08db0d0ff6a3af846466","tid":2031781,"uid":197441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"7d35bc0a3b8a19c72dbbe79e622c7a8ae811c964","tid":2031781,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:02:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後想請大家簽一簽以下聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=cc0852ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"7a4e69374d14a59c7d9518ac4329900d6faa4a64","tid":2031781,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/k